{"tid":1002361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大專女教師返家　揭財經顧問男友燒炭亡","createTime":"2019-01-31T01:14:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T03:53:07.000Z","uid":160807,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"520390b68ba2f56232798965dd175e77562dc205","tid":1002361,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T01:14:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190131/large/1548867902_dc50.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190131%2Flarge%2F1548867902_dc50.jpg&h=520f2869&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n土瓜灣道35至41號宏豐大廈一單位，近凌晨零時，一名姓邱男子(36歲)在房間床上燒炭昏迷，同居姓陳女友(33歲)返家發現，連忙報警。救護員到場將男事主送院搶救，惜告不治。<br />\n<br />\n據稱，死者為財經顧問，屬自僱人士，女友在大專院校任教師，兩人準備今年結婚。警方發現單位門窗用膠紙封着，旁邊有燒炭的器皿和炭灰。警方在場沒有撿獲遺書，調查事件無可疑。"},{"pid":"3cdc1e36253bde9138fd768f866e1e032bc2b4e6","tid":1002361,"uid":55533,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T01:17:12.000Z","msg":"金融才俊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04467248ecbbf5789ad9b7b09f3ada8b9b216003","tid":1002361,"uid":190540,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T01:19:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eee734ac869fa63434ba7703a91ca5b72b4ab088","tid":1002361,"uid":200641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T01:19:19.000Z","msg":"係咪姐係倫敦金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d14e5fb513a1db1a670031fe5a2b1590f0c3fc17","tid":1002361,"uid":21398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T01:19:25.000Z","msg":"升返都要自殺？"},{"pid":"4b99fa2da99d53cf4ddfd26b83e209e8d0772914","tid":1002361,"uid":211461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d14e5fb513a1db1a670031fe5a2b1590f0c3fc17","tid":1002361,"uid":21398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T01:19:25.000Z","msg":"升返都要自殺？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T01:29:33.000Z